Thresholding¶

In [3]:
img4, img2, img3 = get_lanes(img)

def plot(img2, img3, img4):
    f = plt.figure(figsize=(24, 9))
    ax1 = f.add_subplot(1, 3, 1)
    ax1.imshow(img2, cmap = 'gray')
    ax2 = f.add_subplot(1, 3, 2)
    ax2.imshow(img3, cmap='gray')
    ax3 = f.add_subplot(1, 3, 3)
    ax3.imshow(img4, cmap='gray')
    
plot(img2, img3, img4)

Lanes Detection¶

In [5]:
laneLines = LaneLines()
img6, img5 = laneLines.forward(warped_img)

def plot(img5, img6):
    f = plt.figure(figsize=(24, 9))
    ax1 = f.add_subplot(1, 2, 1)
    ax1.imshow(img5, cmap = 'gray')
    ax2 = f.add_subplot(1, 2, 2)
    ax2.imshow(img6, cmap='gray')
    
plot(img5, img6)
